    "description": {
        "": "Generates matched Perfect Print driving + driven gears as solid bodies (reductions, step-ups, or 1:1, any tooth counts >= 6); the driven gear has an elliptical Perfect-Print tip (lower tip interference/friction) and is left free to swing about the driving gear so you can align it with existing features"
    },
